        <title>使用 FDD 框架分析《The Case of the Golden Idol》</title>
        <link>http://localhost:1313/p/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-fdd-%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90the-case-of-the-golden-idol/</link>
